lead_paragraph: Coach Tom Herman and No. 6 Houston insist they won't be looking past Lamar despite the quick turnaround they'll face with their American Athletic Conference opener against Cincinnati looming next Thursday.

headline.print_headline: No. 6 Houston Has Quick Turnaround After Facing Lamar
